Here's how the config options are used:

- commands/hooks
   - Passed to external commands
   - No newlines
- external
   - Filename
   - No newlines
- need newline
   - Text written to an email
   - Anything allowed
   - Written to file, displayed by the pager
- menu
   - Text line in a Menu
   - All whitespace transmuted to space (0x20)
   - `print_enriched_string()`
- status bar
   - Text on a status bar
   - All whitespace transmuted to space (0x20)
   - `mutt_draw_statusline()`
- custom
   - Written to Window directly
   - All whitespace transmuted to space (0x20)
   - `sb_repaint()`

